0.25_01 2011.8.29
    - Exposed wxEVT_STC_INDICATOR_CLICK, wxEVT_STC_INDICATOR_RELEASE,
      wxEVT_STC_AUTOCOMP_CANCELLED and wxEVT_STC_AUTOCOMP_CHAR_DELETED events
